# .gitignore — LevFin Book project
# Keeps version control to the real deliverables; excludes junk and temp files.

# --- Microsoft Office lock files (created automatically while a file is open) ---
~$*.docx
~$*.xlsx
~$*.xls
~$*.pptx

# --- LibreOffice lock files (created during recalc / PDF conversion) ---
.~lock.*#

# --- Operating-system / sync junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# --- Python artifacts (from model-editing / recalc scripts) ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/

# --- Temp & conversion artifacts ---
*.tmp
*~
slide-*.jpg
thumbnails.jpg

# --- Editor / IDE settings ---
.vscode/
.idea/
